\newlabel{fig:comm_overview}{{5}{19}{Communication performance across transmission rates. (a) Total dropped packets as a function of requested rate, showing packet loss only at low frequencies. (b) Measured receive rate versus requested transmission rate, demonstrating approximately linear tracking}{figure.caption.10}{}}
